    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/44eae3087d18736d778147c775595dbb.poster.avif?t=1761154337\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/44eae3087d18736d778147c775595dbb.webm?t=1761154337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/44eae3087d18736d778147c775595dbb.mp4?t=1761154337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/c6e004746d0d941c5d27750454f3d1c9.avif?t=1761154337\" width=594 height=177 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/19c466c26b1e0aecb606e67b64993faa.webp?t=1761154337\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/19c466c26b1e0aecb606e67b64993faa.poster.avif?t=1761154337\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=186 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore the graveyards of GHOST GOLFING!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⛳At the start of each level, the hole is there, lonely, on the other side of the field, and you have a series of pieces that form the path to it. There are windmills, pumpkins, gravestones, mirrors, and even portals! Your challenge? Build the perfect path to guide the ball! And believe me, it won't be easy. One misplaced piece, and the ball could end up rolling off the field or flying straight into the lake!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/d3ec94c547bc477a922c9b3272531962.apng?t=1761154337\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/d3ec94c547bc477a922c9b3272531962.poster.avif?t=1761154337\" class=\"bb_img\" width=595 height=295 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👻The fun increases with each world! Explore the graveyards: 'Will this curve work here? What if I place a bonfire right before this ice block? Does the pumpkin explode?' Only after setting everything up can you take your shot and hope the ball follows the right path. And when it finally drops into the hole after passing through your crazy creations, the feeling of victory is incredible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/8c1636b4d292a7286563c2c458432622.poster.avif?t=1761154337\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/8c1636b4d292a7286563c2c458432622.webm?t=1761154337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/8c1636b4d292a7286563c2c458432622.mp4?t=1761154337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎃 <strong>GHOST GOLFING</strong> is part golf, part puzzle, and 100% fun. Are you ready to build the path of your dreams (or your nightmares)?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/abe40f30b1b08ee00c2656f9c2abca18.poster.avif?t=1761154337\" width=595 height=295 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/abe40f30b1b08ee00c2656f9c2abca18.webm?t=1761154337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/2a50026a63ef7c96b6d1653f67da6dda.webp?t=1761154337\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206510/extras/2a50026a63ef7c96b6d1653f67da6dda.poster.avif?t=1761154337\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=248 /></picture></span></h2>",
